author: Allan Smith
title: 'Lock her up!': Anti-Whitmer coronavirus lockdown protestors swarm Michigan Capitol
description: Thousands of Michiganders descended on the state capitol in Lansing on Wednesday to protest Gov. Gretchen Whitmer's recent enhancement of the state's stay-at-home order.
content:
Demonstrators descended on the state Capitol in Lansing on Wednesday to protest Gov. Gretchen Whitmer's restrictive stay-at-home order, clogging the streets with their cars while scores ignored organizers' pleas to stay inside their vehicles.
